Package: restless
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: reactive API discovery and Unix automation runtime
 Restless is a terminal-native developer utility for safe API surface
 discovery, topology inspection, and filesystem-triggered command execution.
 .
 It performs bounded discovery using safe HTTP methods, stores local session
 state, renders API structure, and can run shell commands reactively when
 watched files change.
 .
 Restless is designed for Unix composition: small commands, inspectable output,
 shell pipelines, and local-first workflows.
